      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As for the motorcycle crash scene, it wasn’t discovered until another driver hit the bike, which was still on the road but was laying on its side. That driver stayed at the scene and called police. Later, they discovered the rider’s body in a ditch by the road.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
